**The drawing could depict a teenage boy sitting on the edge of a skyscraper with his feet dangling off the edge. He's wearing casual clothing, with a backpack by his side and a laptop open in his lap. The cityscape sprawls out behind him, with towering buildings and busy streets.Beneath him, there is a thick blanket of fog, obscuring the view of the ground far below. The fog creates a sense of mystery and danger, emphasizing the precariousness of his position.The boy himself could be shown with a sense of calm and confidence, as though he's done this many times before. Perhaps he's a skilled hacker, working on a complex project that requires him to be in this high-up location. Or maybe he's just seeking solitude and a break from the hustle and bustle of the city below.The overall atmosphere of the drawing could be somewhat surreal and dreamlike, with muted colors and a sense of stillness despite the bustling cityscape in the background.** - <@420532380303097857> (fast)
